## Testes com Promptfoo

```yaml
# .nexoritia/evals/promptfoo/sop-retrieval.yaml
prompts:
  - 'Dado o contexto: {{context}}
     Responda: {{query}}'

tests:
  - vars:
      query: "Qual o procedimento de limpeza?"
    assert:
      - type: contains
        value: "POP.001"
      - type: contains
        value: "detergente neutro"
```

